Package: wiggleplotr
Title: Make read coverage plots from BigWig files
Version: 0.1
Author: Kaur Alasooo [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Kaur Alasoo <kauralasoo@gmail.com>
Description: Tools to visualise read coverage from sequencing experiments together with genomic annotations (genes, transcripts, peaks). Introns of long transcripts can be shrunken to a fixed length for better visualisation of exonic read coverage.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.2)
Imports:
    plyr,
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    GenomicRanges,
    rtracklayer,
    cowplot,
    assertthat,
    purrr,
    S4Vectors,
    IRanges,
    GenomeInfoDb
License: Apache License 2.0
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
